    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The whole app is a completely self-contained, 300-line Python script, most of which is machine learning code. In fact, there are <a href="https://github.com/streamlit/demo-self-driving/blob/master/app.py" target="_self">only 23 Streamlit calls in the whole app</a>. You can run it yourself right now!</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
